<h3>About Tracks</h3>
<p>Learning sales tracking has never been easier using Tracks and it’s amazing drag and drop interface. Tracks is focused on helping small businesses keep up to date with monthly sales and revenue that integrates with both Highrise CRM and Google Apps.</p>
