<h3>Challenges</h3>
<p>This project was not without it's challenges in multiple cases. It was required to create a dynamic calendar picker for custom selections that display dates in a very particular fashion. For this we hired the help of <a href="https://shanehudson.net">Shane Hudson</a>.</p>
<figure class="figure-site" style="margin: 0;">
	<img src="{{site.imgdir}}clients/tracks/datepicker.gif" alt="">
	<figcaption><small>Timeline Datepicker</small></figcaption>
</figure>
<p>This custom datepicker leverages the power of <a href="https://bevacqua.github.io/rome">Rome</a> as a base and config that is combined with a custom <a href="https://bitbucket.org/grayghostvisuals/tracks/src/da226bb268769ee6e523220e986c124fa48dd9c8/js/src/datepicker.js?at=datepicker&fileviewer=file-view-default">JS file</a> to create special conditions and filtering in order to return the correct selections.</p>
<p>Other challenging spects were flexbox layout implementations as cross-browser was extremely fragile. To solve this issue with odler browsers we reverted to table display to ensure layouts did not break. Creating <b>isolated components and case studies</b>, <b>naming conventions<b>, <b>color swatch picker</b>, draggable card sorting and motion design.</p>

